ttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadmCj7d.gif&h=c2976eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n忍得好辛苦就喊咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"香港鬼殺隊(海外)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:16:11.000Z","msg":"爛牙蛭"},{"pid":"7614cbd55e321c2df30bfbf4aee7f342612fbeae","tid":2437141,"uid":36383,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9fe2ddf3215824bb82c4b48715ce382955350ce","tid":2437141,"uid":50931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"細良國父係咪收左共產黨錢想批鬥世柒老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"支持住世蛭老師，細良都係鬼<br />\n世蛭只是個孩子呀"},{"pid":"495b26ab2a76575ac3b9373eddd9507611ef838e","tid":2437141,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">搬石頭張六常，PR 網軍專門發佈 BNO 假消息、分化 BNO 手足 及 國際線，見字勿回，感謝。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據如下：</ins><br />\n<br />\n====搬石頭張六常 [常駐：校園台]====<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/36383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/36383</a><br />\n<br />\nPOST 1: [時間已證明六常是對的] BNO 苦 主 後 悔 移 英 ： 返 唔 到 香 港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2385148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2385148</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用英國資薪水平，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實英國最低工資水平遠高於香港，而且藍白領工種之間工資差距水平極低，尊重不同行業。雖然稅收較香港高，但同時有全民醫療同退休保障，長遠生活成本較香港低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPOST 2: 如果你自問學歷差冇經驗冇錢冇乜體力又想要舒服日子，建議留返香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2387307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2387307</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用英國工作機會攻擊英國，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實現時英國失業率較香港低，因為封城反而帶旺部份行業需求，另外英國疫苗注射效率極高，長遠英國工作機會因為武肺問題消退及脫歐人口流失而大幅提升</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPOST 3: [勸世2] 英國滿歧視，移民屬不智<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2378847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2378847</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">分析：用外國人會歧視人攻擊英國，阻止人到英國</span><br />\n*事實英國英國本身已經有大量第一二代移民，甚至國家重要官員唔少都係移民後代<br />\n最近英國更有大量協助港人既組織相繼成立：e.g. <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2405905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2405905</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 此人同時擔任分化國際線既工作<br />\n攬炒巴 + 重光團隊只係可有可無嘅人，炒作兩條蛋散係冇咩價值<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380384</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">拉</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSORUCE:<br />\n請問張六常(欣客)(狗隻#36383)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2325823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2325823</a>"},{"pid":"7d75cdf4bc44ef5afe98b7e73ea2826fe2f6d5ad","tid":2437141,"uid":36383,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"樓上條傻狗一講蝗細蛭就沖入黎<br />\n歐洲 5 點半食晚餐見到張六常追擊 post 嬲到震？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aed21cfe951c7b9fbac477dd894ab2cd81227cb","tid":2437141,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"細蛭呀細蛭，唔好以為匿埋德國冇人識你，我都係德國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8422c5e8bc8b9c02ced35b0d793a272e7854bbea","tid":2437141,"uid":34666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1aed21cfe951c7b9fbac477dd894ab2cd81227cb","tid":2437141,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"細蛭呀細蛭，唔好以為匿埋德國冇人識你，我都係德國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"納粹德國有無請猶太警察殺自己同胞呢臭閪蚑那賤蛆<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a168d231baf56e56dcb10de67e899438195fce","tid":2437141,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":2,"scor